|[[File:BG MuraVenete 08.JPG|150x150px|alt=City walls.]]
| {{sort|ZZZ|[[Lombardy]], [[Veneto]], [[Friuli]], ''also: ''<br>{{flag|Croatia}}<br/>{{flag|Montenegro}}}}
| {{convert|378.37|ha|abbr=values|sortable=on}}; buffer zone {{convert|1,749.62|ha|abbr=values}}
| {{sort|2017|1533; 2017; iii, iv}}
